===================================================================

Context:
  The CONTRIBUTING.md file was carried over from the previous "Ontos" project
  and contained outdated references (repo URLs, tooling, scope descriptions,
  license type, frontend stack). Rewrote it to accurately reflect the
  OntoBricks project.

Changes:

1. ``CONTRIBUTING.md`` — Replaced all "Ontos" references with "OntoBricks".
2. ``CONTRIBUTING.md`` — Updated repo URLs to ``databrickslabs/ontobricks``.
3. ``CONTRIBUTING.md`` — Replaced Hatch/Yarn tooling with uv-based workflow.
4. ``CONTRIBUTING.md`` — Removed React/TypeScript frontend references; aligned
